text:
TV Magazine 'I don't know how Lauren can take him back!' Michelle Keegan laughed at Mark Wright’s ‘cringe’ romance with Lauren Goodger – four years before SHE married him 
The former Corrie beauty didn't have a very high opinion of Mark before she met and fell in love with him By REBECCA POCKLINGTON
